d medium Industries.\n\nCiccarelli is the founder and president of Malpractice Foundation, a not-for-profit organisation that defends the rights of the victims of medical malpractice. It provides free legal assistance. It is the only Foundation in the world that covers against trial risks.\n\n==Publications==\nHe is author of many works, including:\n* ''Sustainable Development and International Law'' (2000)\n* ''Project Finance in Italy'' (2001) [https://web.archive.org/web/20110722032240/http://www.denaro.it/VisArticolo.aspx?IdArt=272816&KeyW=CICCARELLI%20ANTONIO%20KIM]\n* ''Property Management and Asset Management''(2001) [https://web.archive.org/web/20110722032220/http://www.denaro.it/VisArticolo.aspx?IdArt=260916&KeyW=CICCARELLI%20ANTONIO%20KIM]\n* ''Innovative Finance'' (2002)'\n* ''Trust'' (2002) [https://web.archive.org/web/20110722033116/http://www.denaro.it/VisArticolo.aspx?IdArt=266398&KeyW=OLTREMARE]\n* ''Reit \u2013 Real Estate Investment Trust'' [https://web.archive.org/web/20110722032255/http://www.denaro.it/VisArticolo.aspx?IdArt=270707&KeyW=CICCARELLI%20ANTONIO%20KIM]\n* ''Private Equity'' (2002) [https://web.archive.org/web/20110722032322/http://www.denaro.it/VisArticolo.aspx?IdArt=281640&KeyW=CICCARELLI%20ANTONIO%20KIM]\n* ''STU Societ\u00e0 di Transformazione Urbana'' (2005) [https://archive.is/20121209174444/http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:nnOgESflMdEJ:www.comune.montesilvano.pe.it/immagini/news/1-ADULTI.doc+ciccarelli+antonio+kim&cd=5&hl=it&ct=clnk&gl=it&lr=lang_it&client=firefox-a]\n* ''Manual of Finance for Innovation'' (2008) [https://web.archive.org/web/20111004181124/http://www.ibs.it/code/9788889278062/ciccarelli-antonio-k-ciccarelli/manuale-di-finanza-per.html]\n* ''The Dreams in the Economy of the Twentieth Century'' ( 2008)\n* ''Manuale di Finanza per l'innovazione'' (2008);[https://web.archive.org/web/20110718093748/http://www.deastore.com/libro/manuale-di-finanza-per-l-innovazione-antonio-k-ciccarelli-nicola-v-cic